through emoting through sound.

00:30:00.489 --> 00:30:02.650
By mirroring that we can begin to get

00:30:02.650 --> 00:30:04.555
a sense of what someone else feels,

00:30:04.555 --> 00:30:05.977
the beginnings of empathy maybe.

00:30:05.977 --> 00:30:08.601
So it could be both ontogenetically

00:30:08.601 --> 00:30:10.742
and maybe phylogenetically,

00:30:10.742 --> 00:30:15.475
music was a crucial part on
the journey towards language.

00:30:15.475 --> 00:30:17.723
- Stay up here cause I wanna
