In your talk you have
mentioned people with semantic

00:33:20.511 --> 00:33:21.511
I think it's

00:33:22.694 --> 00:33:27.002
dementia making a mistake
about colors of animals.

00:33:27.002 --> 00:33:30.087
Does this imply that language determines

00:33:30.087 --> 00:33:32.156
that the thesis that language
determines our information

00:33:32.156 --> 00:33:34.323
processing and categories.

00:33:36.417 --> 00:33:38.509
- I think yes, I mean.

00:33:38.509 --> 00:33:42.916
I think we see really two
sort of degenerative models

00:33:42.916 --> 00:33:44.196
for this.

00:33:44.196 --> 00:33:48.683
One is when the left side
