and semantic knowledge,

00:34:16.291 --> 00:34:19.851
the sort of knowledge that we
start layering on as children.

00:34:19.851 --> 00:34:24.458
And I think this is the
nidus of the degeneration and

00:34:24.458 --> 00:34:26.905
semantic variant and you do lose

00:34:26.905 --> 00:34:30.405
