00:41:22.669 --> 00:41:25.843
that in his imagination plays other

00:41:25.843 --> 00:41:28.641
real college basketball teams.

00:41:28.641 --> 00:41:30.402
And he does this on a regular basis,

00:41:30.402 --> 00:41:32.347
and he's done this
since he's 13 years old.

00:41:32.347 --> 00:41:34.501
He's now 60 years old.

00:41:34.501 --> 00:41:36.584
And from time to time I get a news release

00:41:36.584 --> 00:41:39.191
